import React from 'react'; import { FaLaptop, FaMobileAlt, FaServer, FaCogs, FaBrain, FaDatabase, FaArchive, FaChartLine } from 'react-icons/fa'; const BrainzArchitecture = () => { return (

Brainz Architecture

Scalable and Modular AI-Powered Application Architecture

{/* Frontend Layer */}

Frontend

Web Interface

Responsive React-based user interface with modern design system and component library.

{/* Backend Layer */}

Backend

API Gateway

Central entry point for all client requests, handling routing, authentication, and rate limiting.

/api/v1/chat
/api/v1/train
/api/v1/models

Microservices

Modular services for user management, content processing, analytics, and notifications.

AI/ML Services

Machine learning models for natural language processing, recommendations, and personalization.

{/* Data Layer */}

Data

Database

Scalable database cluster with read replicas for high availability and performance.

Object Storage

Secure and durable storage for user uploads, media files, and static assets.

{/* Data Flow */}

Data Flow

1

User Interaction

User interacts with the web or mobile interface

2

API Processing

Request is authenticated, validated, and routed

3

Service Execution

Appropriate microservices process the request

4

Data Persistence

Data is stored and processed in the appropriate data stores

); }; export default BrainzArchitecture;
